headline: Navigator Holdings (NVGS) Beats Q4 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Navigator Holdings (NVGS) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 18.75% and 4.22%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: What privatizing the US Postal Service could mean for prices, coverage
summary: As President Donald Trump mulls big changes for the agency, experts said taking it private could put some of its current advantages at risk.
